---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---

<SiteLayout
  title="nelsonkwesi.xyz — Stop doing the same thing twice."
  description="The follow-ups your team forgets. The admin that eats mornings. The calls nobody answers. We build the systems that handle all of it."
  activeNav="home"
>
  <style>
    /* Hero */
    .hero { padding: 52px 0 44px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); position: relative; }
    .hero::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; left: 0; right: 0; top: 28%; height: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(240,192,48,0.07) 30%, rgba(240,192,48,0.14) 50%, rgba(240,192,48,0.07) 70%, transparent);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .hero-inner { padding: 28px 28px 24px; }
    .sys-line {
      font-size: 0.58rem; color: var(--amber-dim); letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 20px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    }
    .sys-line::before { content: '>'; color: var(--amber); }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4.5vw, 3.1rem); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.06;
      color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 16px;
      text-shadow: 0 0 28px rgba(240,192,48,0.12);
    }
    .hero h1 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--amber); text-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(240,192,48,0.45); }
    .hero-desc { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--ink-dim); line-height: 1.82; max-width: 560px; margin-bottom: 28px; }
    .hero-note { display: block; font-size: 0.56rem; color: var(--ink-faint); margin-top: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
    .vhs-stamp { position: absolute; bottom: 14px; right: 18px; font-size: 0.52rem; color: var(--amber-dim); letter-spacing: 0.08em; opacity: 0.55; }

    /* Case studies */
    .case-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1px; background: var(--border); margin-top: 24px; }
    .case-card { background: var(--bg); padding: 24px; }
    .status-badge { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-size: 0.52rem; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .status-badge.live { color: var(--amber); }
    .status-badge.live::before { content: '●'; animation: blink 1.4s step-end infinite; color: var(--amber); }
    .status-badge.done { color: rgba(100,230,100,0.85); }
    .status-badge.done::before { content: '■'; color: rgba(100,230,100,0.85); }
    .case-section-heading { font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem) !important; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.1; }
    .case-card h3 { font-size: 0.92rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 8px; line-height: 1.2; }
    .case-card p { font-size: 0.63rem; color: var(--ink-dim); line-height: 1.72; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .case-items-label { font-size: 0.5rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--amber-dim); margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .case-items { list-style: none; }
    .case-items li { font-size: 0.6rem; color: var(--ink-dim); padding: 4px 0; border-top: 1px solid rgba(240,192,48,0.07); display: flex; gap: 8px; }
    .case-items li::before { content: '>'; color: var(--amber); flex-shrink: 0; }

    /* Audit CTA */
    .audit-box { border: 1px solid var(--amber); position: relative; }
    .audit-box-label { position: absolute; top: -9px; left: 16px; background: var(--bg); padding: 0 8px; font-size: 0.52rem; letter-spacing: 0.16em; color: var(--amber); text-transform: uppercase; }
    .audit-inner { padding: 28px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; gap: 28px; align-items: center; }
    .audit-inner h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .audit-inner h2 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--amber); }
    .audit-desc { font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--ink-dim); line-height: 1.78; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .chips { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 5px; }
    .chip { font-size: 0.55rem; letter-spacing: 0.07em; color: var(--ink-faint); border: 1px solid rgba(240,192,48,0.12); padding: 3px 10px; }
    .price-block { text-align: center; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .price { font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--amber); text-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(240,192,48,0.38); line-height: 1; }
    .price-sub { font-size: 0.52rem; color: var(--ink-faint); letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 14px; display: block; }

    /* About teaser */
    .about-inner { max-width: 600px; }
    .about-inner p { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--ink-dim); line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .about-inner p:last-of-type { margin-bottom: 0; }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .case-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .audit-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="box">
      <span class="box-label">INIT //</span>
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <p class="sys-line">Software Engineer &middot; Business Systems Builder</p>
        <h1>Stop doing the<br/>same thing <em>twice.</em></h1>
        <p class="hero-desc">
          The follow-ups your team forgets. The admin that eats every morning.<br/>
          The calls nobody answers at lunch. The deals lost because nobody followed up.<br/>
          Nine years building software. Now I build the systems that handle all of it.
        </p>
        <a class="btn" href="/ai-audit">Find What's Stealing Your Time &middot; $500</a>
        <span class="hero-note">30-min call &middot; we build the fix live &middot; you leave with a plan</span>
      </div>
      <span class="vhs-stamp">CH:01 &nbsp;&#9654; PLAY</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- What We Build -->
  <div class="section">
    <p class="sec-label">SYSTEM LOG // WHAT WE FIX</p>
    <h2>Real problems. Fixed in public.</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">
      Most businesses lose hours every day to things that should handle themselves.
      We build the systems that fix that and document everything live, so you can
      see exactly how it works before you commit to anything.
    </p>
    <div class="tags">
      <span class="tag">Missed Follow-ups</span>
      <span class="tag">Content on Autopilot</span>
      <span class="tag">Rental Ops That Run Overnight</span>
      <span class="tag">Admin That Does Itself</span>
      <span class="tag">Business Audits</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Case Studies -->
  <div class="section">
    <p class="sec-label">CASE STUDIES // LIVE BUILDS</p>
    <h2 class="case-section-heading">Problems we're solving, live.</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Real businesses. Real fixes. Not finished, but running.</p>
    <div class="case-grid">
      <div class="case-card">
        <span class="status-badge live">IN PROGRESS</span>
        <h3>The Rental That<br/>Runs Overnight</h3>
        <p>Guests message at midnight. Cleaners need scheduling. Reviews pile up. This rental business handles all of it without a property manager on call. Human oversight stays. The repetitive ops are gone.</p>
        <p class="case-items-label">WHAT STOPPED BEING MANUAL</p>
        <ul class="case-items">
          <li>Guest and tenant messages answered 24/7, check-ins included</li>
          <li>Cleaners and contractors hired automatically via Thumbtack and Angi</li>
          <li>Maintenance requests routed to the right person without a call</li>
          <li>Review responses written and posted without anyone touching them</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="case-card">
        <span class="status-badge done">LIVE SYSTEM</span>
        <h3>One Topic In.<br/>A Week of Content Out.</h3>
        <p>A content team used to take a week to do what this system does in an hour. One topic goes in. Scripts, lead magnets, and posts come out. Every format. Every platform. Nobody staring at a blank page.</p>
        <p class="case-items-label">WHAT STOPPED BEING MANUAL</p>
        <ul class="case-items">
          <li>Finding what the audience actually complains about, pulled fresh every 30 days</li>
          <li>Scripts with 3 hook variations so the best one gets filmed</li>
          <li>PDF lead magnets generated from the best-performing scripts</li>
          <li>Full Notion pipeline from idea to posted, nothing tracked by hand</li>
          <li>Top performers auto-saved to an inspiration library for future use</li>
          <li>Blog, carousel, and repurposed formats output in the same run</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- AI Audit CTA -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="audit-box">
      <span class="audit-box-label">// AUDIT</span>
      <div class="audit-inner">
        <div>
          <h2>Tell me what's<br/>eating your <em>week.</em></h2>
          <p class="audit-desc">
            You talk, I listen, I build. In 30 minutes you'll see exactly what's been
            draining your team's time, and leave with a working fix. No jargon.
            No homework. No pitch deck.
          </p>
          <div class="chips">
            <span class="chip">30-MIN ZOOM</span>
            <span class="chip">FIX BUILT ON THE CALL</span>
            <span class="chip">ONE-PAGE REPORT</span>
            <span class="chip">3 NEXT STEPS</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="price-block">
          <div class="price">$500</div>
          <span class="price-sub">FOUNDING RATE</span>
          <a class="btn" href="/ai-audit" aria-label="Book an AI Audit — $500">Book Now &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- About Teaser -->
  <div class="section">
    <p class="sec-label">// ABOUT</p>
    <div class="about-inner">
      <p>Born in Ghana. Moved to the US for college. Spent close to a decade building software: JavaScript, TypeScript, backend systems, banking platforms.</p>
      <p>Then got serious about what these tools could actually do in production. Not prototypes. Real systems running real businesses. Started building two of them and documenting everything publicly.</p>
      <p>Steve Jobs didn&apos;t just build the thing. He made people understand why it mattered. That&apos;s the idea here. We build, we share, we figure it out together.</p>
      <div class="socials">
        <a class="social" href="https://x.com/nelsonkwesix" target="_blank" rel="noopener">X: @nelsonkwesix</a>
        <a class="social" href="https://youtube.com/@nelsonkwesi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">YouTube: Nelson Kwesi</a>
        <a class="social" href="https://instagram.com/nelsonkwesi.xyz" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram: @nelsonkwesi.xyz</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</SiteLayout>
